    <item>
      <title>藐视南非领导人祖马的普拉温·戈尔丹去世，享年 75 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/pravin-gordhan-who-defied-south-african-leader-zuma-dies-at-75</link>
      <description><![CDATA[普拉温·戈尔丹 (Pravin Gordhan) 去世，享年 75 岁。他曾担任南非内阁的三个职位，并在雅各布·祖马 (Jacob Zuma) 丑闻缠身的总统任期内敢于反抗，赢得了赞誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/pravin-gordhan-who-defied-south-african-leader-zuma-dies-at-75</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 04:16:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反犹主义丑闻在选举前引起立陶宛领导人的警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/antisemitism-scandal-alarms-lithuanian-leaders-ahead-of-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛下个月将举行议会选举，该国主要政治力量联合起来反对一个新政党的崛起，该政党的领导人因反犹太言论而接受审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/antisemitism-scandal-alarms-lithuanian-leaders-ahead-of-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡反对党候选人希望重新谈判国际货币基金组织贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/sri-lanka-opposition-candidate-wants-to-renegotiate-imf-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡主要反对派领导人表示，如果他赢得下周的总统大选，他将与国际货币基金组织就 30 亿美元贷款重启谈判，以减轻工薪阶层的经济负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/sri-lanka-opposition-candidate-wants-to-renegotiate-imf-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 03:33:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑客袭击台湾证券交易所和大型银行，引发神秘外国攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/hackers-hit-taiwan-bourse-major-bank-in-mystery-foreign-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，黑客攻击了台湾的金融平台，包括证券交易所和兆丰金控股份有限公司，导致其网站短暂中断，当地媒体称这是外国代理机构的攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/hackers-hit-taiwan-bourse-major-bank-in-mystery-foreign-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 02:59:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>医疗危机担忧 尹永哲支持率再创新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/yoon-s-support-rate-at-new-low-amid-concerns-over-medical-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心数千名医生因抗议政府的改革计划而失业，给医疗系统带来压力，韩国总统尹锡烈的支持率跌至2022年上任以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/yoon-s-support-rate-at-new-low-amid-concerns-over-medical-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 02:45:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜首次公开铀计划 成为美中摩擦焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/north-korea-make-first-display-of-uranium-program-at-center-of-us-friction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜首次公布了原子弹用铀浓缩设施的照片，照片显示领导人金正恩参观了该项目的核心工厂，该项目已成为朝鲜与美国 20 多年来的摩擦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/north-korea-make-first-display-of-uranium-program-at-center-of-us-friction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 23:36:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普承诺不对加班税征税，争取蓝领选民投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/trump-pledges-no-taxes-on-overtime-in-pitch-to-blue-collar-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党人唐纳德·特朗普在辩论表现不佳几天后的一次集会上承诺取消加班税，这位总统候选人希望通过一项新的民粹主义减税方案翻开新的一页。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/trump-pledges-no-taxes-on-overtime-in-pitch-to-blue-collar-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 23:01:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工会“坚决”反对，称美国钢铁交易“注定失败”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/us-steel-deal-with-nippon-called-doomed-by-steelworkers-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国钢铁工人联合会表示，它不会被迫接受新日本制铁公司为收购美国钢铁公司而争取工人支持的最后一搏，称这笔价值 141 亿美元的收购是一笔“注定失败的交易”，并誓言要抵制任何外国对该公司所有权的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/us-steel-deal-with-nippon-called-doomed-by-steelworkers-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 22:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
